{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't know what a vitamin pill was and I traded it off to a baker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, I want a half a loaf every day, and forever and forever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I only lasted with this guy 10-- 10 days because he got-- he got shipped out to Auschwitz, poor bastard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- but at least-- and then people said, how can you sell vitamins?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've got no vitamins, your teeth are falling out, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like you know, you could have taken your-- there was absolutely no value in the food we were getting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people explained to me, you were crazy to give this guy the vitamins, you should-- you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, my stomach is hungry and I wanted the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- so-- so they cleaned up the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started planting flowers and-- and they had the women scrub the-- the sidewalks and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had this one particular street near the-- where it was really cleaned up and that's where they took the-- they took the inspectors.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I at that time, when all the people got shipped out, all of a sudden, we had animals in our camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And and the reason we had horses and cows and chickens and oxen was because there was a city in Czechoslovakia called Lidice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the city-- after Heydrich was assassinated in Prague, the Germans took the city, the small city, and killed all the males.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the men were killed in the camp, all the women and children were put in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The children were put to-- into-- young children were put into German families so they completely forgot what they were.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
